<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.1.8">
<l>mācūṇāc cuṭaruṭampāy malarātu kuviyātu</l>
<l>mācūṇā ñāṉamāy muḻutumāy muḻutiyaṉṟāy</l>
<l>mācūṇā vāṉkōlat tamararkōṉ vaḻippaṭṭāṉ</l>
<l>mācūṇā vuṉapāta malarcōti maḻuṅkātē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being a glowing body that does not absorb stains, being knowledge that does not absorb stains,</l>
<l>not blossoming, not piling, being the whole, being made of the whole,</l>
<l>if the king of the immortals praises [your] heavenly beauty that does not absorb stains,</l>
<l>the light of the foot blossoms of you who does not absorb stains will not become dull.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
